               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) The Sǝnkǝssar for the first half of the year (fols. 4ra-237ra)&#xD;
                     I-1) Maskaram (fols. 4ra–42vb) &#xD; I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 43ra–75vc)&#xD; I-3)
                     Ḫǝdār (fols. 76ra–113rc)&#xD; I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols. 114ra–155vc) &#xD; I-5) Ṭǝrr
                     (fols. 156ra–202vc)&#xD; I-6) Yakkātit (fols. 203ra–237ra)&#xD; The
                     commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns&#xD; &#xD; Additio
                     1.</summary>
